resource":"databasePage","operation":"create","databaseId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Request Database"},"title":"={{ $json.query || $json.requestId }}","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[9693,1420],"id":"82833347-1421-4648-9316-af82f8a333ff","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf01291-request`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Required Fields Present?","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"9423cea7-dec9-5041-409d-04d563f5f2ff","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Required Fields Present?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.query }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Detect Sentiment · ②→ Abort — Malformed Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"d18ef39e-89fd-2fa9-d0c5-c912c5e885cd","name":"Note: Required Fields Present?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Abort — Malformed Input\n\nFails fast with a clear message; triggers the error workflow instead of processing bad data.","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,1030],"id":"09a5f904-b8d8-4ea9-632f-0cde9b9ae5e7","name":"Note: Abort — Malformed Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Detect Sentiment\n\nScores the text's sentiment; ports fire positive / neutral / negative.\n\nPorts: ①→ Escalate Negative — Gmail · ②→ Log Neutral Feedback, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Thank the Sender\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"2c9ff197-271c-4382-aba5-e92aa805ba90","name":"Note: Detect Sentiment"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Detect Sentiment** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1090],"id":"b881f552-8c71-5c14-82fc-8860eb73a3ae","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Negative — Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,40],"id":"7703a15a-be2f-6a8e-a15e-f2819b3dc6ae","name":"Note: Escalate Negative — Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Log Neutral Feedback\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,520],"id":"f4b6a5c9-adfa-f415-cfc6-506893b0a1d7","name":"Note: Log Neutral Feedback"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Thank the Sender\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Collect All Outcomes · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,1000],"id":"76d15907-ecf0-d232-a0e9-4bfd16471c5f","name":"Note: Thank the Sender"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Collect All Outcomes\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2505,520],"id":"fb9b23bf-f62d-50da-20a2-7097aa076c36","name":"Note: Collect All Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"2104fb0b-ecd1-88f7-23df-b2e2f76a80fa","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"f721039a-ac89-3603-740c-eca66f1164cb","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\nnotion — `getAll` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"26c1ed8e-f0b3-97ab-d183-6624a976571c","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Enrich with Reference Data","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"30d981a3-c882-adaa-5364-f8e3ec6de160","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"7ecf56cf-1953-f07f-cd27-511d1b1d50f5","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,520],"id":"d1704a90-b773-2803-b2a0-4bcf741ded51","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5745,520],"id":"cd489cc0-55c0-45d9-fc10-76f3b1840c6d","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6069,520],"id":"0129e42a-95d9-c291-a831-9d91e8a2646d","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6393,520],"id":"aad0280f-0e74-8258-03ba-cedc9845eeb6","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fingerprint for Idempotency · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6717,520],"id":"4d23de7a-0d70-e208-fed6-9b1bb3d0b38c","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per request (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7041,520],"id":"47411ddf-0376-07fe-d8ff-23bb679a3775","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty query","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7365,520],"id":"e1719927-d5d7-5d93-3f28-68010f78a68c","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty query\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7689,520],"id":"fd8be109-e250-645f-7a63-03cc1a1e1d75","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty query"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8013,520],"id":"b5ad8fac-56d8-281b-cf0e-427e5d262760","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Sort Requests Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8337,520],"id":"ae9570f8-518c-0854-a4db-e94e7f8c7f1a","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Requests Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8661,520],"id":"b12eb264-5da8-26ff-374a-dbcdf2860487","name":"Note: Sort Requests Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8985,520],"id":"f6ceb958-b542-6351-3822-c0a1a9999d69","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9309,520],"id":"42f5c4fe-be25-f989-04c3-0974b9f6fc8b","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9633,520],"id":"c7dc23d2-a15b-009c-413b-512e1a2541c4","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[8985,1540],"id":"985c76f8-3643-9f6d-8388-3dc3fd35967f","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9309,1540],"id":"4cf849b5-5593-150f-bcd7-6872db0b2a60","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[9633,1540],"id":"5bb84096-db4a-0483-5f75-60416e1c2e34","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Summarize long emails with Google Sheets and Gmail with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nSummarize long emails with Google Sheets and Gmail with instant alerts. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual multi-tool agent is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Required Fields Present? → Detect Sentiment → Escalate Negative — Gmail → Collect All Outcomes → Stamp Completion Time → Persist Run Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating multi-tool agent in ai\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"da93d0fd-3bbe-c37b-67b2-95802736ef92","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"a8731424-e2df-37e7-c656-604d6c81e5c8","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"6d073826-9a35-d301-22f8-5459408faadc","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"eeedcf49-4992-ef34-8d14-0b265bbe3f25","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your multi-tool agent process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-500],"id":"8fd5e860-1d7a-da8a-961d-5e7ff9691311","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Required Fields Present?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Required Fields Present?":{"main":[[{"node":"Detect Sentiment","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Abort — Malformed Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Detect Sentiment","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Detect Sentiment":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Negative — Gmail","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Log Neutral Feedback","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Thank the Sender","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Negative — Gmail":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Log Neutral Feedback":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Thank the Sender":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect All Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Collect All Outcomes":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty query","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty query":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Requests Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Requests Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"f7158801-297e-4d64-84c5-da32c45a9fa6","id":"FDX01291"}